title: Ring of Fire - September 21 2013
description:
September 21, 2013
Ring of Fire 
Hosted by Robert F. Kennedy Jr., Mike Papantonio and Sam Seder


This week on Ring of Fire Radio: 

Hour 1: Discussions on news stories that the Corporate controlled media outlets refuse to talk about.

Hour 2: John Nichols from The Nation will tell us how progressive uprisings are changing American politics from the bottom up. And Author David Kirby will discuss the ethical implications of keeping killer whales in captivity.
